reviewText: Played just fine! I would highly recommend this if you're a Brandis fan.
Arians is gorgeous. Poor Jonathan Brandis. Took his own life.

A fun movie that's great for the whole family. It is a product of the 90's made for TV film craze though so it's not the best acting, plot, or cinematography, however, the kids won't really notice due to the cute baby lions.
In no way can it be compared to 'Born Free'.However,as a lover of wild life movies,I have watched it just. DVD quality is very good.
